open

public java.util.Map<java.io.File,AutoTagger> open(java.io.File[] availablePlugins,
                                                   java.io.File[] curPlugins)
Shows the GUI for automatic tagging algorithms selection. This GUI displays algorithm data as well.

Parameters:
availablePlugins - The plugins available for loading.
curPlugins - The plugins which should be marked as loaded already.
Returns:
Files of chosen automatic taggers and their classes. null is returned if the user chose to abandon changes.
